data.description: Recently renovated FOUR SIDES BRICK ranch in convenient location!Newer, low maintenance luxury vinyl plank flooring and carpet in bedrooms. Spend more time living and less time cleaning in this functional, easy to maintain 2 bedroom and 2 full bath layout. Easy access to downtown, shopping and schools as well as I75 and the city of Atlanta yet tucked away surrounded by peaceful, mature shade trees.
